# PDF Password Mappings
# Map sender email addresses or domains to decryption passwords
# 
# Format options:
# - Exact email match: "sender@example.com": "password"
# - Domain wildcard: "*@example.com": "password"
# - Default fallback: "*": "default_password" (optional)

# Examples:
# "billing@electricity.com": "electricity123"
# "*@telecom.com": "telecom2024"
# "*": "default_password"  # Use if all PDFs share same password